            "id": 6429608,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 費城半導體大漲1.83%，報9823.75點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間22日09:30，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>上漲176.53點（或1.83%），暫報9823.75點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+4.59%</li><li>近 1 月：+25.77%</li><li>近 3 月：+19.96%</li><li>近 6 月：+41.06%</li><li>今年以來：+36.2%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>成分股以美光科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MU-US</a>)領漲。美光科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MU-US</a>)上漲3.98%；英特爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>)上漲3.42%；英特格(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ENTG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ENTG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ENTG-US</a>)上漲3.4%；連貫(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:COHR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/COHR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">COHR-US</a>)上漲3.28%；萊迪思半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:LSCC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/LSCC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">LSCC-US</a>)上漲3.18%。</p></section></main>",
